Borden Inc called redemption March 23 outstanding 8-1/2 pct sinking fund debenture , due 2004 .
The company said redemption price 104.55 pct face value plus 40.61 dlrs accrued interest October 1 , 1986 redemption date , making total 1,086.11 dlrs 1,000 dlrs face value .
The trustee Bank America National Trust Savings Association San Francisco paying agent Bankers Trust Co , New York .
